english_items = [
    ('词汇', '高考核心词汇分类记忆与高级替换', '名词核心：抽象类(advantage, benefit, consequence, influence, impact, phenomenon, situation, approach, attempt, effort)；具体类(device, facility, alternative)。<br>动词核心：表达类(express, convey, indicate, demonstrate, reveal, reflect, suggest, imply)；变化类(change, transform, alter, modify, shift, vary, adjust)；引起类(cause, give rise to, lead to, result in, bring about, contribute to)。<br>形容词核心：positive/negative, significant/essential/beneficial/harmful/effective/available/reasonable/considerable。<br>副词核心：however, therefore, thus, consequently, moreover, furthermore, nevertheless, meanwhile, eventually, gradually, particularly, specifically。<br>高级词汇替换：important→essential/significant/vital/crucial；good→beneficial/positive/favorable/remarkable；bad→harmful/negative/adverse/undesirable；big→massive/enormous/significant/considerable；think→believe/argue/maintain/claim/hold the view that；many→numerous/a variety of/a wide range of；because→due to/owing to/on account of/as a result of；but→however/nevertheless/whereas/yet；so→therefore/thus/accordingly/consequently；very→extremely/highly/greatly/fairly。<br>搭配能力：动词+名词(make/do/take/have/give/pay)；形容词+名词；介词搭配。<br>构词法（派生）：-tion/-sion/-ment/-ness/-ity表名词；-able/-ible/-ful/-less/-ous/-ive/-al/-ary表形容词；-ly表副词；en-/-en-/-ize/-ise表动词；un-/in-/im-/dis-/mis-表否定；re-再；pre-/post-前后；anti-反对；inter-之间；super-超级；trans-转变。<br>构词法（合成）：名词+名词=复合名词(bookstore, website, smartphone)；形容词+名词=复合名词(fastfood, greenhouse)；动词+副词=复合名词(breakthrough, output, input)；形容词+现在分词=复合形容词(hardworking, good-looking)。<br>构词法（转化）：water n.水→v.浇水；hand n.手→v.传递；empty adj.空的→v.倒空；better adj.→v.改善；cool adj.→v./n.。<br>常见短语动词：break系列(break down/up/out/off/through/in)；bring系列(bring up/about/back/forward/out/in)；call系列(call off/on/up/for/in)；come系列(come up/across/about/out/down to)；get系列(get up/on/off/along/through/down to)；give系列(give up/out/in/off/away/back to)；go系列(go up/down/out/on/off/through/over/with)；look系列(look up/down/on/for/into/through/after)；make系列(make up/for/out/up for/of)；put系列(put up/off/on/out/up with/forward/through)；take系列(take up/on/off/out/over/in/after)；turn系列(turn up/down/on/off/out/to/over/into)。<br>易混词辨析：affect（v.影响）vs effect（n.效果/v.实现）；raise（vt.举起/养育）vs rise（vi.上升）；arise（vi.出现/问题产生）；lie（lay/lain躺、lied/lied说谎）vs lay（laid/laid放置/下蛋）；sit（sat）vs set（set放置/设定）；hanged（绞死）vs hung（悬挂）；economic（经济的）vs economical（节俭的）；historic（有历史意义的）vs historical（历史的/与历史有关的）；respectable（值得尊敬的）vs respectful（尊敬人的）vs respective（各自的）；sensitive（敏感的）vs sensible（明智的）；adapt（适应/改编）vs adopt（采用/收养）vs adept（熟练的）；principal（adj.主要的/n.校长/本金）vs principle（n.原则）；stationary（静止的）vs stationery（文具）；desert（沙漠/v.抛弃）vs dessert（甜点）；loose（松的）vs lose（丢失）。<br>记忆策略：词根词缀记忆、分类联想记忆、语境记忆、词块记忆、艾宾浩斯遗忘曲线复习。'),
    ('语法填空', '语法填空高频考点系统归纳', '题型特点：一篇200词左右短文，10空，考点覆盖词法句法。<br>考点一：冠词（a/an/the）。泛指用a/an（元音开头an），特指用the。常见：a/an+adj.+n.；the+比较级（两者中更……的）；the+姓氏复数（一家人）。<br>考点二：介词。常见搭配：①时间介词（in/on/at/since/for/by/during/through）②地点介词（in/on/at/to/off/along/across/through）③固定搭配（depend on, focus on, comment on, result in, lead to, due to, owing to, account for, be known for/as/to, be good at, be interested in）。<br>考点三：代词。①人称代词主格/宾格（I/me, you/you, he/him, she/her, it/it, we/us, they/them）②物主代词（my/mine, your/yours, his/his, her/hers, its/its, our/ours, their/theirs）③反身代词（myself, yourself, himself, herself, itself, ourselves, yourselves, themselves）④不定代词（some/any, many/much, few/a few, little/a little, all, both, either, neither, none, one, each, every, other, another）⑤it用法（形式主语、形式宾语、强调句型、指代时间/距离/天气）。<br>考点四：非谓语动词。①to do（不定式：表目的、将来、作主语/宾语/定语/状语/补语）②doing（动名词/现在分词：表主动进行、作主语/宾语/定语/状语/补语）③done（过去分词：表被动完成、作定语/状语/补语）。<br>重点非谓语句型：It is + adj. + for/of sb. to do；It is no use/good doing；It takes sb. time to do；feel like doing；cannot help doing/to do；have difficulty/trouble (in) doing；look forward to doing；devote...to doing；be used to doing；prefer doing to doing；suggest/advise/consider doing；allow/permit/forbid sb. to do；make/let/have sb. do；see/hear/watch/notice sb. do/doing；with+宾语+to do/doing/done（独立主格）。<br>考点五：从句。①定语从句（who/whom/whose/which/that/as关系代词；where/when/why关系副词。注意非限定性从句用which不用that；介词+which/whom）②名词性从句（主语从句、宾语从句、表语从句、同位语从句。引导词that/if/whether/what/who/whom/whose/which/when/where/why/how/whatever/whoever/whichever）③状语从句（时间when/while/as/since/before/after/until/till/as soon as；条件if/unless/once/provided；让步though/although/even if/however/whatever/no matter；原因because/as/since/now that；目的so that/in order that；结果so...that/such...that；比较as...as/than；方式as/as if；地点where/wherever）。<br>考点六：时态语态。常用时态：一般现在时（主动do/does，被动am/is/are done）、一般过去时（did/was were done）、一般将来时（will do/be going to do；will be done）、现在进行时（is/am/are doing；is being done）、过去进行时（was/were doing；was being done）、现在完成时（have/has done；have/has been done）、过去完成时（had done；had been done）、现在完成进行时（have/has been doing）。<br>时态判断：根据时间状语、上下文语境、逻辑关系。<br>考点七：词性转换。①名词→形容词（use→useful/useless；care→careful/careless；nature→natural；tradition→traditional；danger→dangerous）②形容词→名词（important→importance；different→difference；happy→happiness；safe→safety）③形容词→副词（加ly：quick→quickly；careful→carefully；去e加ly：true→truly；变y为i加ly：happy→happily；特殊：good→well）④动词→名词（加ment/tion/sion/ing/er/or：develop→development；educate→education；decide→decision；mean→meaning；teach→teacher）。<br>考点八：形容词副词比较级最高级。①单音节/部分双音节：+er/+est或特殊（good→better→best；bad→worse→worst；many/much→more→most；little→less→least；far→farther/further→farthest/furthest；old→older/elder→oldest/eldest）②多音节：more/most+原级。<br>重点句型：as+原级+as；比较级+than；the+比较级+of the two；the+最高级+范围；比较级+and+比较级（越来越）；the+比较级,the+比较级（越……越……）。<br>答题步骤：①读全文把握大意②分析句子结构③判断词性④确定具体形式⑤检查时态语态单复数。'),
    ('短文改错', '短文改错常见错误与技巧', '题型特点：一篇约100词短文，10处错误，1处正确（有时无）。<br>错误类型（按频率）：动词时态语态错误、名词单复数错误、介词错误、冠词错误、代词错误、形容词副词混用、比较级最高级错误、从句引导词错误、非谓语错误、逻辑错误、缺词多词。<br>动词错误：①时态：上下文时态不一致（如现在时改过去时）②语态：被动没加be③主谓一致：主语单复数与谓语不一致（第三人称单数漏s）④并列结构动词形式不一致。<br>名词错误：可数名词没加复数、不可数名词加了复数、a/an+不可数名词、one/some/each后名词形式错误。<br>介词错误：固定搭配中的介词错误（listen the music→listen to the music）；时间地点介词错用（in a cold morning→on a cold morning）；多余介词或漏介词。<br>冠词错误：泛指漏a/an、特指漏the、不可数名词加a/an、元音开头用a、a an混用。<br>代词错误：人称代词/物主代词/反身代词错误；指代性别/单复数错误；one/ones/it/them使用错误；反身代词与主语不一致。<br>形容词副词混用：系动词后用副词→改形容词；修饰动词用形容词→改副词；修饰全句应该用副词。<br>比较级最高级错误：原级与比较级混用；more/most与比较级最高级重复（more better）；比较级前没加the的情况。<br>从句引导词错误：定语从句that/which/who/where/when误用；what引导名词性从句；if与whether辨析；which与what引导名词从句差异。<br>非谓语错误：to do/doing/done用错；介词后接动词原形→接doing；并列结构非谓语形式不一致。<br>逻辑错误：and→but；so→but；but→however；肯定否定误用；语义矛盾。<br>缺词：名词前缺冠词、及物动词后缺宾语、系动词缺表语、固定短语缺词。<br>多词：冗余的冠词/介词/代词/连接词、不定式前多余的to。<br>常正确的：高级词汇、复杂结构、难以一眼判断的地方。<br>答题技巧：逐句分析主谓宾定状补→检查各类可能错误→通读检查→注意常见陷阱（hard→hardly；late→lately；most→mostly；already→yet）。'),
    ('阅读理解', '阅读理解各类题型解题攻略', '题型分类：细节理解题、推理判断题、词义猜测题、主旨大意题、作者态度意图题。<br>应用文解题（A篇）：广告、通知、说明书、海报、指南。特点：信息密集、有小标题、含数字价格时间。技巧：先看题目再找答案→关键词定位→注意大写专有名词数字符号→排除干扰项。<br>细节理解题特点：考查对具体事实的把握。常见提问：Which of the following is true/mentioned? According to the passage, who/what/when/where/why/how...?<br>细节题解题：①通读全文理解大意②关键词定位原文③对照选项仔细比较④注意同义替换与反向表达。<br>正误判断题技巧：看清TRUE/NOT TRUE/MENTIONED/NOT MENTIONED/EXCEPT/INCLUDE。<br>推理判断题特点：不是原文直接信息，需分析推断。常见提问：It can be inferred from the passage that... The author implies/suggests that... What can we learn/conclude from...? What is implied but not stated?<br>推理题解题三不原则：①不要选直接原句（那是细节不是推理）②不要选过度推断（超出文章范围）③不要选与常识相符但文章无依据。<br>词义猜测题技巧：①定义法（that is, namely, in other words）②举例法（such as, for example）③对比法（but, however, unlike, while）④因果法（because, so, therefore）⑤构词法（词根词缀）⑥上下文语境⑦指代关系（it/this/that指代前文）。<br>主旨大意题技巧：①看标题/首段/末段②找高频词/关键词③看各段首句④注意首段转折后的内容⑤记叙文看故事寓意⑥议论文看论点⑦说明文看说明对象和特点。<br>常见干扰：①以偏概全（只概括某段）②过度扩大（范围太大）③无中生有④偷换概念。<br>选标题题：选最凝练、最核心、最有吸引力的。<br>作者态度题：积极类（positive, optimistic, approving, supportive, favorable, sympathetic, appreciative, enthusiastic）；消极类（negative, pessimistic, disapproving, critical, skeptical, suspicious, doubtful, opposed, worried, disappointed）；中立类（objective, neutral, impartial, indifferent, ambiguous, cautious, matter-of-fact, uninterested）。<br>态度判断方法：看作者用词的感情色彩（褒义/贬义/中性）、看论点偏向、看特殊符号和引号。<br>七选五解题：①看位置（段首→主题句；段中→过渡句；段尾→总结句）②找关键词（原词/同义词/近义词/上下义词）③找过渡词（however, therefore, moreover, besides, for example, in other words, that is, on the contrary, in contrast）④看逻辑关系⑤代入验证。<br>阅读理解通用策略：①快速浏览抓主旨②仔细阅读找细节③推理判断不武断④词义猜测看语境⑤主旨大意看首尾⑥作者态度看用词⑦干扰选项常陷阱（张冠李戴、偷换概念、以偏概全、无中生有、因果倒置、过于绝对、曲解原意）。'),
    ('完形填空', '完形填空解题技巧与逻辑分析', '完形特点：一篇200-300词短文，20空，考查词汇、语法、语境、逻辑。<br>解题步骤：①通读全文掌握主旨（跳过空格，关注首段）②逐句分析先易后难（语法搭配词汇逻辑）③复读全文验证答案（通顺性、连贯性）。<br>语境解题：根据上下文暗示→前呼后应→前后文信息互补。<br>逻辑解题：转折(but, however, yet, although, though, instead, on the contrary)、因果(because, for, as, since, therefore, so, thus, consequently, as a result)、递进(moreover, furthermore, besides, in addition, also, too, what is more, worse still)、并列(and, or, as well as, both...and, either...or, neither...nor, not only...but also)、对比(while, whereas, on one hand...on the other hand, some...others...)。<br>复现解题：原词复现、同义词复现、反义词复现、上下义词复现、结构复现。<br>搭配解题：①动词固定搭配(take advantage of, make use of, pay attention to, take into consideration/account, attach importance to, play a role/part in, have an effect/influence/impact on)②形容词介词搭配(be good at, be interested in, be satisfied with, be concerned about/for, be responsible for, be aware of, be capable of, be consistent with)③名词介词搭配(key to, answer to, solution to, reason for, cause of, attitude towards/to, approach to)。<br>情感色彩解题：作者感情基调（褒义/贬义/中性）决定选词方向。<br>记叙文完形：关注故事时间线、人物关系、事件发展、情感变化、结尾升华。<br>议论文完形：关注论点论据、逻辑连接、作者立场。<br>说明文完形：关注说明顺序、事物特征、因果关系。<br>高频词汇：动词(manage, try, attempt, offer, afford, promise, persuade, allow, permit, admit, remind, realize, recognize, accept, receive, achieve, accomplish, succeed, fail, remain, stay, leave, keep, hold, support, maintain, survive, recover)；名词(opportunity, chance, choice, alternative, decision, effort, attempt, purpose, aim, goal, target, intention, desire, passion, courage, wisdom, strength, ability, talent, skill, experience, knowledge, information, message, announcement, statement, comment, opinion, view, attitude, behavior, manner, action, activity)；形容词(willing, eager, anxious, nervous, curious, patient, generous, modest, proud, ashamed, embarrassed, confused, puzzled, shocked, astonished, amazed, surprised, excited, delighted, pleased, satisfied, disappointed, frustrated, exhausted, relieved, relaxed, comfortable, convenient, available, accessible, affordable, reasonable, reliable, responsible, professional, efficient, effective, successful, valuable, important, essential, significant, necessary, beneficial, harmful, dangerous, risky, safe, secure, certain, sure, likely, possible, probable, common, ordinary, general, normal, regular, usual, frequent, rare, unique, special, particular, specific, individual, personal, private, public, social, cultural, historical, traditional, modern, advanced, ancient, natural, artificial, digital, virtual, realistic, practical, theoretical, academic, scientific, technical, technological, economic, political, environmental, educational, medical, industrial, agricultural, commercial, financial, legal, moral, ethical, spiritual, mental, physical, emotional, psychological)。<br>最后复读：检查语法通顺、逻辑合理、主旨明确。'),
    ('书面表达', '书信格式与各类书信及高级句型', '英语书信格式：①信头（发信人地址日期，右上角）②称呼（Dear..., 左侧）③正文（分段写）④结尾敬语（Yours sincerely/faithfully/truly, 右下）⑤签名。<br>高考常考书信：道歉信、感谢信、建议信、申请信、投诉信、邀请信、询问信、介绍信、推荐信、祝贺信、慰问信、通知。<br>道歉信：①说明道歉事由②解释原因（不找借口）③提出补救措施④再次道歉请求谅解。常用语：I am writing to apologize for...; I feel terribly sorry that...; Please forgive me for...; I promise that...; To make up for...。<br>感谢信：①表达感谢②说明感谢的具体事情③评价这件事的意义④再次表达感谢或希望回报。常用语：I am writing to express my sincere gratitude for...; I would like to convey my heartfelt thanks to you for...; Without your help, I would never have...; I really appreciate what you have done for me。<br>建议信：①说明写信目的②提出具体建议（2-3条）③解释为什么这样建议④希望建议被采纳。常用语：I am writing to share my suggestions on...; I would like to offer some advice on...; Here are my suggestions/advice/tips/recommendations; First... Besides... Furthermore...; I hope you will find these suggestions helpful。<br>申请信：①说明申请什么及信息来源②自我介绍（个人情况/教育/经验/能力）③表达愿望与承诺④附相关材料请求回复。常用语：I am writing to apply for...; I am writing in response to your advertisement for...; I would like to apply for the position/post of...; I graduated from...; I have experience in...; I am good at.../I have a good command of...。<br>邀请信：①说明邀请事由②邀请谁参加③活动时间地点内容④期待对方接受邀请。常用语：I am writing to invite you to...; I wonder if you could come to...; It would be a great honor for us if you could...; The activity will be held on...at...; I really hope you can make it。<br>通知：标题NOTICE、发布单位、日期时间、事件、地点、对象、注意事项、联系方式。常用语：There will be a... to be held on...; All the students are welcome to...; Anyone who is interested in... please...; Please be present on time; Please sign up before...。<br>演讲稿：①开场白（问候+自我介绍+主题）②主体（分点阐述）③结尾（总结+感谢）。常用语：Good morning/afternoon/evening, ladies and gentlemen; I am honored to have the opportunity to speak to you today about...; Today I would like to talk about...; First of all... Secondly... Last but not least...; In conclusion/To sum up/In short...; Thank you for your attention。<br>倡议书：①倡议背景/原因②倡议的具体内容/做法③呼吁大家参与④表达决心。常用语：Nowadays, ... is becoming more and more...; It is high time that we...; Here are some suggestions for us to follow; First... Second... Third...; I hope all of us will...; Let us take action right now!。<br>议论文写作：①提出观点②论证（举例/引用/因果/对比）③总结升华。正反观点型：开头引入→观点一+理由→观点二+理由→个人观点。<br>高级句型提升：倒装句（Never/Seldom/Little/Hardly/Rarely/Only.../So.../Such...置于句首）；强调句（It is/was + 被强调部分 + that/who + 其他）；虚拟语气（If I were you/If it had not been for/I wish/I would rather）；分词作状语（Having done.../Done...）；with复合结构（with + n./pron. + to do/doing/done/adj./adv./prep.）；非谓语动词开头（To do... is.../Doing... is...）；定语从句（which/who/that/where/when/why引导）；名词性从句（what/that/whether/whatever引导）；状语从句（though/if/because/so...that引导）；并列句（and/but/so/or/for连接）。<br>高级词汇运用：用significantly替代very；用beneficial替代good；用consequently替代so；用nevertheless替代but；用numerous替代many；用a wide range of替代different kinds of。<br>连接过渡词：表递进(furthermore, moreover, besides, in addition, what is more, additionally)；表转折(however, nevertheless, nonetheless, yet, but, on the contrary, in contrast, by contrast, conversely)；表因果(therefore, thus, consequently, as a result, because of this, due to this, for this reason, hence, accordingly)；表列举(first, first of all, to begin with, in the first place, second, besides, in addition, furthermore, moreover, what is more, finally, last but not least, eventually)；表举例(for example, for instance, such as, like, take... for example, a case in point is, as an illustration, to illustrate)；表总结(in conclusion, in summary, in short, in brief, all in all, to sum up, in a word, overall, generally speaking)；表对比(on one hand...on the other hand, for one thing...for another, in comparison with, compared with/to, by comparison, by contrast)；表强调(indeed, in fact, actually, as a matter of fact, certainly, definitely, absolutely, obviously, apparently, evidently, clearly, particularly, specifically, especially, notably, most importantly, above all, first and foremost, primarily, chiefly)；表时间(at present, currently, now, these days, nowadays, today, recently, lately, in recent years, in the past few decades, at the same time, meanwhile, in the meantime, simultaneously, eventually, finally, ultimately, in the end, at last, previously, formerly, earlier, before, prior to, after, afterwards, later, following, subsequent, next, then, after that, from then on, from now on, in future, in the future, soon, shortly, in the near future, immediately, instantly, right now, right away, at once, promptly, as soon as possible, the moment, the minute, the instant, hardly...when, no sooner...than)。<br>作文高分要点：①内容完整要点齐全②结构清晰层次分明③语法正确错误少④表达多样句式丰富⑤词汇高级搭配地道⑥书写工整卷面整洁⑦字数恰当（100-120-150词）。')
]

